{"tid":2038501,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［檢討post］香港人，你哋係咪真係想建國？","createTime":"2020-05-27T15:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T00:24:50.000Z","uid":312193,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ee25e2de33d22f3e6f3d98c3a131abc0d7dce014","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR: 香港人如果要建國，就一定要有犧牲嘅決心</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n相信愈嚟愈多香港人都認同：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 建國</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個<span style=\"color: gold;\">國家</span>，至少都會有自己嘅<span style=\"color: maroon;\">軍隊</span><br />\n一隊<span style=\"color: maroon;\">軍隊</span>，將軍<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會</span>同士兵講：<span style=\"color: orange;\">人冇事先做到世界冠軍</span><br />\n<br />\n但我哋成日同手足講：<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">be water</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">人冇事先做到世界冠軍</span><br />\n<br />\n我明白，我哋<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔想失去任何一個手足</span><br />\n但事實係次次行動都<span style=\"color: brown;\">會俾黑警拉幾百個手足</span><br />\n又會<span style=\"color: brown;\">俾黑警毆打、掃射</span><br />\n之前亦都<span style=\"color: brown;\">有唔少手足輕生</span><br />\n咁樣落去真係唔得掂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我唔想我哋次次出去都俾狗打俾狗拉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果香港人真係想建國：</span></span><br />\n之後每次行動要當<span style=\"color: red;\">打仗</span>一樣 <br />\n點解要係我哋俾<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警</span>捉<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">點解唔可以係我哋捉黑警</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">嗌咗黑警死全家咁耐<br />\n點解一個黑警都冇死過</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我哋一定要俾班狗知道<br />\n佢哋做嘅嘢係有代價嘅</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">贏</span>，就要有<span style=\"color: red;\">犧牲</span>嘅決心<br />\n就算<span style=\"color: red;\">贏唔到</span>，都會<span style=\"color: red;\">攬抄</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">曼德拉</span>曾經講過：<br />\n「如果我殺咗你，我要<span style=\"color: brown;\">坐監</span>，但你已經<span style=\"color: red;\">死</span>咗」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要記住，喺香港國入面<br />\n我哋先係兵，班狗係賊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港人，你準備好建國了嗎？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人冇事先做到世界冠軍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算要我死都要建國<br />\n歡迎理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354cc51a70438747cebf8658addf26a671cda27b","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"9623177ab6e2e62e71d05043886217218cba2ba9","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"bb620ffd0c731e0f565b4e3eac48fe259d641c54","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:10:08.000Z","msg":"香港人 建國"},{"pid":"ccaa0ef6015f5c4bf53ae9ae65253ad272050946","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de1d0583461aac2163fc9260f443ee26814d8d12","tid":2038501,"uid":47189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee25e2de33d22f3e6f3d98c3a131abc0d7dce014","tid":2038501,"uid":312193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR: 香港人如果要建國，就一定要有犧牲嘅決心</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n相信愈嚟愈多香港人都認同：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 建國</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一個<span style=\"color: gold;\">